CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "Thoroughbreds - Mrs. Dewey Abrams of Bryn Mawr Road is owner of these Afghan hounds, Chupressi, left, and Tachi. Both dogs are considered champions.  Tachi won top honors last year in Stubenville Dog Show - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Two Afghan hounds, Chupressi and Tachi, posed in front of brick house or building, front view
